{"version": 2, "width": 80, "height": 24, "timestamp": 1774000369, "idle_time_limit": 3.0, "env": {"SHELL": "/bin/bash", "TERM": "xterm-256color"}, "title": "Multi-Agent Orchestration: 5 Modules Refactored in Parallel"}
[0.003615, "o", "╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗\r\n║  Multi-Agent Orchestration: 5 Modules in Parallel           ║\r\n║  ACGS-Lite Constitutional Governance Engine                  ║\r\n"]
[0.003877, "o", "╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝\r\n\r\n"]
[2.004491, "o", "━━━ PHASE 1: Module Analysis ━━━\r\n\r\n"]
[3.00546, "o", "→ Scanning module sizes...\r\n"]
[3.506408, "o", "\r\n  Module              Lines   Files\r\n  ─────────────────── ─────── ─────\r\n  constitution/       32,875    ~60\r\n  integrations/        3,587     ~8\r\n"]
[3.506499, "o", "  compliance/          2,853     ~6\r\n  eu_ai_act/           1,954     ~5\r\n  engine/              1,817     ~4\r\n\r\n  Total: 43,086 lines across 5 modules\r\n\r\n"]
[5.507412, "o", "━━━ PHASE 2: Spawning 5 Sub-Agents in Parallel ━━━\r\n\r\n"]
[6.508506, "o", "  🔀 Agent[constitution] → worktree isolation, branch refactor/constitution\r\n  🔀 Agent[integrations] → worktree isolation, branch refactor/integrations\r\n  🔀 Agent[compliance] → worktree isolation, branch refactor/compliance\r\n  🔀 Agent[eu_ai_act] → worktree isolation, branch refactor/eu_ai_act\r\n"]
[6.508608, "o", "  🔀 Agent[engine] → worktree isolation, branch refactor/engine\r\n\r\n"]
[7.509468, "o", "  Each agent independently:\r\n    1. ruff check --select E,W,F (lint)\r\n    2. mypy --ignore-missing-imports (types)\r\n    3. Add docstrings to public APIs\r\n"]
[7.509569, "o", "    4. Generate tests for uncovered exports\r\n    5. pytest -x to verify green\r\n    6. Commit on its branch\r\n\r\n"]
[9.510507, "o", "  ⏳ All 5 agents running concurrently...\r\n"]
[11.511483, "o", "\r\n  ✓ Agent[constitution]  — 14 files, 23 type fixes, 11 docstrings, 17 tests\r\n"]
[11.812499, "o", "  ✓ Agent[integrations]  — 12 files, 11 type fixes,  6 docstrings, 14 tests\r\n"]
[12.1135, "o", "  ✓ Agent[compliance]    —  3 files, 10 lint fixes,  10 docstrings, 23 tests\r\n"]
[12.414443, "o", "  ✓ Agent[eu_ai_act]     —  6 files,  1 type fix,   10 docstrings, 61 tests\r\n"]
[12.715415, "o", "  ✓ Agent[engine]        —  3 files, 32 type fixes,  9 docstrings, 18 tests\r\n\r\n"]
[14.716394, "o", "  🔍 Critical finding: integrations agent discovered a real bug\r\n     anthropic.py: strict=False silently ignored at 5 call sites\r\n\r\n"]
[16.717436, "o", "━━━ PHASE 3: Merge All Branches ━━━\r\n\r\n"]
[17.718444, "o", "→ git checkout -b refactor/combined\r\n"]
[18.219407, "o", "→ git merge refactor/engine --no-edit\r\n  Fast-forward (4 commits: constitution, integrations, engine, compliance)\r\n"]
[18.720394, "o", "→ git merge refactor/eu-ai-act --no-edit\r\n  Merge made by 'ort' strategy — no conflicts\r\n\r\n  ✓ All 5 branches merged cleanly. 0 conflicts.\r\n\r\n"]
[20.721485, "o", "━━━ PHASE 4: Full Test Suite on Merged Result ━━━\r\n\r\n"]
[21.722479, "o", "→ python -m pytest packages/acgs-lite/tests/ -q --import-mode=importlib\r\n\r\n"]
